svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20110222 at Thu Sep 17 12:00:48 2015 By www-data Stem is a geometric sans-serif with semi-closed aperture and large x-height. 12 faces of it, including upright and true italic faces of different weights, are intended primarily for large point sizes. The Stem family will be supplemented with faces for text and caption setting. Design -- Alexandra Korolkova with the assistance of Maria Selezeneva and Isabella Chaeva. Released by ParaType in 2014.
